Package: chipcompare
Title: Compare multiple ChIP-Seq experiments.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Charles", "Joly Beauparlant", role=c("aut", "cre"),
    email="Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca")
Description: By default, chipcompare will calculate the overlap between
    multiple Chip-Seq experiments and represent it as a heatmap.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyData: true
